					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8683669#post-4063623</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8683669/scp-3694#post-4063623</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 20 Nov 2018 14:46:49 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Meserach</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1507289</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Fair enough! The hardest decisions I took on this were a) how much detail of the detail I worked out about the plant's reproductive cycle to include and b) whether it needed more of a payoff in the ending than it now has; I could very easily have decided differently but in the end went with the version that got the most positive reviews from my reviewers.</p> <p>I might spin off some of my cutting room floor ideas into a tale or something, or maybe, if a bunch of people are finding the ending to lack payoff, I'll edit the skip itself. But I'm going to let it sit for a bit before I do either.</p> <p>I appreciate you holding feet to the fire in quality terms though shaggydredlocks , we can always be better, and there's not much point in writing here if I'm not being pushed to improve.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8683669#post-4063281</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8683669/scp-3694#post-4063281</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 20 Nov 2018 05:35:58 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Shaggydredlocks</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1722371</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Needlessly convoluted setup for what the payout is.</p> <p>I mean, I <em>really</em> enjoyed the observation log, don't get me wrong, but for all the detail in how it propagates, it loses out in efficiency, for how much those traits mean very little in the end.</p> <p>This could have simply been the single weird location; lumping on multiple fantastical traits lessened its legitimacy and strained immersion for me.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
