				<wikidot:authorName>ItsDenali</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4284264</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>From concept to execution, it's not hard to tell that a lot of dedication was put into this article, and overall I really enjoy this SCP. The thing that sealed it for me was the use of Denny's over other available restaurant chains, and its clever incorporation into a biological SCP which can oftentimes be a difficult feat.</p> <p>TL;DR: Great job!</p> <p>+1</p> 
				 	]]>
