					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8683669#post-4061911</guid>
				<title>Author post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8683669/scp-3694#post-4061911</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 18 Nov 2018 13:29:41 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Meserach</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1507289</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>My return to skip writing after I was a one hit wonder with <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1442">SCP-1442</a> five years ago, which is a very different kind of article. I didn't imagine my comeback would be anything like this, but such is the magic of <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2320004&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542776010" alt="Rimple" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2320004)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" >Rimple</a></span> 's <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/draft-swap-hub">draft swap.</a></p> <p>This started out as a draft from <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaguebearer" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4364963&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542776010" alt="plaguebearer" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4364963)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaguebearer" >plaguebearer</a></span>, who deserves all the credit for the core concept of a plant Denny's that grows when people shit in parking lots, and the title. Everything else was just me following the logic of Denny's-as-flowering-plant until I found the madness within.</p> <p>I did much of the writing for this on my phone with the flu, so, yeah.</p> <p>So many people did crit and review on this, so I've very probably missed someone. If I missed you, I'm sorry I suck, let me know and I'll put you in and write you a two line poem of apology or something.</p> <p>So, thanks to:<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542776010" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kakroom" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2198340&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542776010" alt="Kakroom" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2198340)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kakroom" >Kakroom</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hotchocletylez" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1933327&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542776010" alt="HotChocletyLez" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1933327)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hotchocletylez" >HotChocletyLez</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2320004&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542776010" alt="Rimple" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2320004)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" >Rimple</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaguebearer" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4364963&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542776010" alt="plaguebearer" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4364963)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaguebearer" >plaguebearer</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542776010" alt="Roget" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" >Roget</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1267048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542776010" alt="Ihp" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1267048)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" >Ihp</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1613974&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542776010" alt="UraniumEmpire" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1613974)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire" >UraniumEmpire</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dysadron" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4384469&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542776010" alt="Dysadron" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4384469)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dysadron" >Dysadron</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=318209&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542776010" alt="DrMagnus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=318209)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" >DrMagnus</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themanhattenproject" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3809943&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542776010" alt="TheManhattenProject" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3809943)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themanhattenproject" >TheManhattenProject</a></span> and t